The paper discusses the quality of code repositories of AI papers hosted on GitHub, which involves software engineering (cs.SE) practices such as code quality, documentation, and maintenance. The paper also focuses on AI technologies (cs.AI) and their implementation in code repositories. Additionally, the paper mentions the difficulty in configuring the underlying runtime environment, which relates to programming languages (cs.PL) and machine learning algorithms (cs.LG). Finally, the paper mentions the lack of documentation and maintenance, which can affect computer vision (cs.CV) research.
